description.displayText: Jaley is helping me with housekeeping/ homesitting whenever we are out of town. Trusting someone with the keys to your house when you are not home is no easy feat, but she is excellent and trustworthy. She checks the lists we provided, make sure everything is complete, and communicates when needed. Great find!

description.displayText: Jaley nannied for us for about two years, and we absolutely loved her! She was super great at engaging with our children and making them feel loved. She stayed off her phone (We have issues with previous nannies on their phone the whole time). We always came home to a clean house. Which was huge for us, and made a big difference. She was always willing to run errands and do miscellaneous things for us. We are sad to see her move but so happy for her!!
